<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00278/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一块型号不明的手机电池，当所处空间温度超过30℃时，该项目会迅速膨胀到汽车安全气囊的大小。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site23东侧的手机修理店<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>保存于Site23的低风险异常项目仓库中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>“一名女士跟我说手机的安全气囊弹出来了，当时我还不信。”——潜伏于手机修理店的邢特工</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00278" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00278" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00278-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ginger249-jackie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4136896); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4136896&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247390" alt="Ginger249-Jackie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4136896)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ginger249-jackie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4136896); return false;">Ginger249-Jackie</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1592710114 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">21 Jun 2020 03:28</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00518/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一件██公司出品的衬衫，会使穿戴者感觉很扎并认为是自己的头发粘在了里面。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>外勤特工luris的家中。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>存放于Area-CN-15的低价值异常物品储藏室内。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>有被冒犯到<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-184219-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-184219-1')">1</a></sup>。&#8212;luris</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00518" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00518" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00518-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kaster-k" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6606914); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6606914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247390" alt="kaster-k" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6606914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kaster-k" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6606914); return false;">kaster-k</a></span></p>
